---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import FastForwardIcon from "@mui/icons-material/FastForward";
import Icon from "@mui/material/Icon";
---

<MainLayout title="Home">
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <!-- <div class="w-screen"> //tried: rausgenommen statt div ohne klasse vorher -->
      <div class="farbcontainerBlue1">
        <p></p>
      </div>
      <div class="farbcontainerBlue2">
        <h1 class="pagetitleStart">the forms_Wizard Project</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="page-main">
      <div class="page-intro">
        <h1 class="leading-relaxed text-center mt-6">
          In civic organizing contexts there are usually few resources and a lot
          of structure is needed to pool the collected energy. <br />
          <a href="/blog"><u>Learn more</u></a> and follow the development process
          of <br />a tool that supports civic engagement in data management.
          <br />
          <br />
        </h1>
      </div>
      <div class="wrap-element-a">
        <div>
          <img
            src="/src/images/iconsFront/noun-empowering-2202388(1).png"
            class="icon-front"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="leading-relaxed text-[#5660ce]">
            The Forms_Wizard aims to supports crews in various use cases to
            collect and evaluate the data they need. This can happen self hosted
            or on our infrastructures.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="wrap-element">
        <div>
          <p class="leading-loose text-[#5660ce] text-right">
            A core part of the WizardPac is the evaluation tool - with the
            DataWizard you can visualize shift plans, show locations on a map,
            evaluate connections on a network graphs and more. <br />Also we
            integrated an interdependence between dataset and visualization so
            that you can effictively make use of the different view ports.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img
            src="/src/images/iconsFront/noun-analysis-3694231(1).png"
            class="icon-front"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="wrap-element-a">
        <div>
          <img
            src="/src/images/iconsFront/noun-cyber-security-3685949(1).png"
            class="icon-front"          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="leading-loose text-[#5660ce]">
            Security by Design is the leading concept in the WizardPac build. In combination with the Open Source distribution you dont need to trust your data into a black box.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="wrap-element">
        <div>
          <p class="leading-relaxed text-[#5660ce] text-right">
            We believe in civic engagement - in times of increasing crises, not
            only in face of the climate catastrophe, we see the necessity of
            individuals organizing in communities. In that menner the whole
            WizardPac transparently and collaboratively build as Open-Source.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img
            src="/src/images/iconsFront/noun-breathe-clean-air-3046872(1).png"
            class="icon-front"          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
